description: Take on tough waste jobs with confidence using our large heavy duty rubble sacks, designed for strength, capacity, and sustainability. Made from recycled materials, these extra heavy-duty sacks are the ideal choice for builders, gardeners, and professionals managing large volumes of waste. Each rubble sack is constructed from thick 100-micron polythene and measures 20" x 30" (508mm x 762mm), offering generous space and durability for demanding tasks. Built to hold up to 30kg of waste, we recommend a safe maximum load of 20kg for long-lasting performance. Whether you're clearing construction debris, trimming hedges, or managing daily garbage, these garden waste bags provide the rugged strength you need. The high-quality build resists tears, splits, and punctures—ensuring secure transport of rubble, grass, soil, sand, and other non-fragile materials. Reusable and available in black and blue designs, these builders bags combine robust functionality with eco-conscious design. They’re made from recycled waste and help reduce environmental impact without compromising on quality. Forget flimsy bin liners—our heavy duty waste sacks are built to simplify clean-up jobs of any size, from site clear-outs to everyday refuse collection.
